    "Non-english results are not relevant, results which are primarily tables are not relevant.",
    "Queries for the dev set were obtained from three internal sources of human research questions, and a set of LLM generations.",
    "We experimented with several methods for constructing the synthetic LLM questions.",
    "Our approach was to generate questions similar to those asked by real users by prompting the LLM to output: (1) a question based on paragraphs retrieved from the corpus, and (2) a \"more general\" version of the first question.",
    "We only use the \"more general\" set since they were more similar to real user queries."
